data.description: This property is situated in a prime location and has a lot of potential for various uses. With a beautiful and large frontage suitable for building, the possibilities are endless. Whether you are looking to develop the land or build residential homes, this property can cater to your needs. You can walk around the property, explore the beautiful surroundings and see if it fits your needs. One of the unique features of this property is that a creek flows through the back, adding to its charm and natural beauty. This adds to the potential for residential development as many people appreciate being close to nature. This property is a must-see if you are looking for a large, well-located, and versatile piece of land. The property will have to be platted before you are able to build residential homes on it.
